Package: UtopiaPlanitia
Title: Variable Importance, Heterogeneity Tests, and Visualization for Causal Forests
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Jack T.", "Rametta", , "jtrametta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9841-146X"))
Maintainer: Jack T. Rametta <jtrametta@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for diagnosing and visualizing causal forests fitted with
    the 'grf' package. Provides leave-one-covariate-out (LOCO) variable
    importance (Benard and Josse, 2023), omnibus Conditional Average Treatment
    Effect (CATE) heterogeneity tests, partial dependence plots, and S3
    summary/plot methods for fitted causal forest objects.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
